channel.title: [WIP] xm8 prototype
channel.description:
Hi guys, this is my 3rd model on these forums. Its untextured at the moment and the pictures here are a little outdated so some of the things you will think look wrong will have changed. I can post a dl link if anybody wants it. I decided to make this because I know how hard it is to find a decent looking model of this gun so i thought 'what the heck I'll make my own'. Made in blender again. I will post updated pictures if I have the time. I know its nothing to do eith runescape or stuff but i want to see what you think of it, please tell me what you think of it and where i can improve.
Enjoy :)
Wireframe [img]http://i1117.photobucket.com/albums/k594/bibbobbib/xm8wire.png[/img]
Edges, verts, faces count [img]http://i1117.photobucket.com/albums/k594/bibbobbib/xm8vertcount.png[/img]
Rendered ( ik it's Flat this is one of the things I changed) [img]http://i1117.photobucket.com/albums/k594/bibbobbib/Xm8rendered.png[/img]
Download link: coming soon to a post near you 8-}
Thanks, leave your thoughts and comments below :-BD
